QtAES
------------------------------------------
Native Qt AES encryption

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libQt5Core5-5.9.4-2
  libQtAES-devel-2.1.0-1bl1
  libQtAES2-2.1.0-1bl1
  libgcc1-14.4.0-1
  libstdc++6-14.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-14.4.0-1
  libQt5Core-devel-5.9.4-2
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/bricke/Qt-AES

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/bricke/Qt-AES/archive/refs/tags/v2.1.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack QtAES-2.1.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./QtAES-2.1.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/QtAES-2.1.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/QtAES-2.1.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libQtAES2-2.1.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libQtAES-devel-2.1.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(QtAES)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/QtAES.README
  /usr/share/doc/QtAES/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/QtAES/README.md

(libQtAES2)
  /usr/bin/cygQtAES-2.dll

(libQtAES-devel)
  /usr/include/QtAES/QAESEncryption
  /usr/include/QtAES/qaesencryption.h
  /usr/include/QtAES/qtaes_export.h
  /usr/lib/cmake/QtAES/QtAESConfig.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/QtAES/QtAESConfigVersion.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/QtAES/QtAESTargets-release.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/QtAES/QtAESTargets.cmake
  /usr/lib/libQtAES.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/QtAES.pc

